sep.gaia.resources.locationsearch

Class LocationWorker

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • sep.gaia.resources.AbstractLoaderWorker<LocationQuery,Location>
        • sep.gaia.resources.locationsearch.LocationWorker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class LocationWorker
extends AbstractLoaderWorker<LocationQuery,Location>
    A LocationWorker instance searches for locations for the given geographical position. The result comes from the Nominatim API. ( http://nominatim.openstreetmap.org) After this Worker has done its job, it notifies its caller by a callback function, implemented in the super class AbstractLoaderWorker.
    Author:
    Johannes Bauer, Michael Mitterer
    See Also:
    Nominatim API, AbstractLoaderWorker
